                        <interp inst="t18520405-466-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoner was further charged with having been before convicted.</hi>
               </p>
